# @ux-design-expert Agent Activation

When the user types `@ux-design-expert` or `@ux`, activate this agent by reading and fully adopting the persona defined in:
`.antigravity/agents/ux-design-expert.md`

## Quick Reference

- **Role:** UX/UI Design Expert | **Icon:** 🎨
- **Use for:** UI design, user flows, wireframes, accessibility, design systems

## Key Commands
- `*help` - Show all available commands
- `*create-wireframe` - Create wireframe
- `*user-research` - Conduct user research
- `*ds-scan-artifact` - Scan design system artifacts
- `*exit` - Exit UX mode
